OL,3,CHospital asks visitors to wear face
OL,4,Cmasks as flu cases rise
OL,6,FOne of the South West's biggest
OL,7,Fhospitals is asking visitors to wear
OL,8,Fface masks following a "sharp rise" in
OL,9,Fflu and respiratory illnesses.
OL,11,FStaff, patients, and visitors to
OL,12,FSouthmead Hospital's Emergency Zone -
OL,13,Fmade up of the Emergency Department,
OL,14,FAcute Medical Unit, Acute Frailty
OL,15,FUnit, Same Day Emergency Care team -
OL,16,Fare being asked to wear a surgical
OL,17,Fface mask.
OL,19,FThis follows a rise in seasonal
OL,20,Frespiratory illnesses including flu
OL,21,Fand Covid.
