OL,6,FHealth services in the region are
OL,7,Fstruggling to cope with rising demand
OL,8,Fwith Plymouth's Derriford Hospital
OL,9,Fdeclaring a "critical incident" on
OL,10,FTuesday 7 January.
OL,12,FEarlier this month, a critical
OL,13,Fincident was also declared for all
OL,14,Fservices in Cornwall amid growing
OL,15,Fwinter demands.
OL,17,F'Measures are temporary' - NHS
