OL,6,FIn a statement, North Bristol NHS
OL,7,FTrust (NBT) said: "In common with NHS
OL,8,Forganisations across the country, NBT
OL,9,Fhas seen a sharp rise in flu and
OL,10,Frespiratory illness over the last few
OL,11,Fweeks ` and in particular since the
OL,12,Fstart of January.
OL,26,@oD@SOU
