OL,6,F"Instead, please contact the ward team
OL,7,Fto discuss alternative options.
OL,9,F"Please be assured that these measures
OL,10,Fare temporary and will only remain in
OL,11,Fforce for as long as they are strictly
OL,12,Fnecessary."
OL,14,F'Only call 999 for life-threatening
OL,15,Femergencies'
OL,17,FSouth Western Ambulance Service is
OL,18,Falso experiencing increasing demand
OL,19,Fand is reminding people to only call
OL,20,F999 in an emergency.
