OL,3,CHospital asks visitors to wear face
OL,4,Cmasks as flu cases rise
OL,6,FMeanwhile, staff at the Royal Devon
OL,7,Fand Exeter Hospital (RDE) are on high
OL,8,Falert as pressure mounts on regional
OL,9,Fservices.
OL,11,FProfessor Adrian Harris, from the RDE,
OL,12,Fsaid: "My first piece of advice is to
OL,13,Fthink very carefully over whether you
OL,14,Fshould call an ambulance.
OL,16,F"Please come to your emergency
OL,17,Fdepartment, your Accident and
OL,18,FEmergency, if you're severely ill and
OL,19,Fdo call an ambulance if it's your only
OL,20,Fway of getting to the hospital.
OL,26,@tD@GOUxD@AOU
