OL,3,CHospital asks visitors to wear face
OL,4,Cmasks as flu cases rise
OL,6,F"But if you can get to the hospital
OL,7,Funder your own steam, please do that.
OL,8,FAlso, please think about whether your
OL,9,Fattendance at the A&E absolutely
OL,10,Fnecessary. Think about 'should I phone
OL,11,F111?', 'should I go to my local
OL,12,Fpharmacy?' or 'would a GP appointment
OL,13,Fbe more relevant?'"
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]
