OL,6,FAsked when the pressure might ease,
OL,7,FProf Harris added: "Historical data
OL,8,Ftells us that we tend to have periods
OL,9,Fthat last between one to two weeks
OL,10,Fwhen we're under these really intense
OL,11,Fpressures and we're about a week in
OL,12,Fnow, so I would be optimistic and
OL,13,Fhopeful that we will come out of this
OL,14,Fsituation in the next few days."
